OL,3,CPolanski declares two-party politics
OL,4,C'dead' after Green mayor elected in
OL,5,CHackney
OL,7,FZack Polanski has said two-party
OL,8,Fpolitics is "dead and buried" after
OL,9,FHackney elected a Green Party mayor in
OL,10,Fa defeat for Labour.
OL,12,FAs votes from local elections are
OL,13,Fstill being counted, the party is
OL,14,Fhoping for further wins in the capital
OL,15,Fand has already gained dozens of
OL,16,Fcouncil seats in England.
OL,18,FZoe Garbett became the Green Party's
OL,19,Ffirst directly-elected mayor, ousting
OL,20,FLabour from the mayoralty it had held
OL,21,Fsince the position was created in 2002.
OL,26,@pD@MOUpD@]O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
