OL,3,CPolanski declares two-party politics
OL,4,C'dead' after Green mayor elected in
OL,5,CHackney
OL,7,FThe Greens have seen a surge in
OL,8,Fsupport since Mr Polanski took over as
OL,9,Fleader last year.
OL,11,FIpsos political director Keiran Pedley
OL,12,Fnoted that even in areas where Reform
OL,13,Fgains seats from Labour, this is
OL,14,Fsometimes down to Labour support being
OL,15,Fdiverted to the Green Party.
OL,17,F"Sometimes it's because of Labour
OL,18,Fsupport going to the Greens and them
OL,19,Flosing votes that way. Then Reform
OL,20,Fsort of comes through the middle," he
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,26,@yD@AOU|D@bO]
